    whyDrHendry: `Dr. Hendry's dual training in Oriental medicine and functional medicine — supported by 25 years of clinical experience — allows him to synthesize information from multiple diagnostic frameworks into a coherent clinical picture. His research background means he can distinguish between conditions supported by strong evidence and those where more cautious interpretation is warranted. This rigor makes the holistic health assessment more clinically useful than a generic wellness evaluation.`,
