    firstAppointment: `Arrive with a clean face — no makeup, SPF, or heavy skincare products. Inform Dr. Hendry of any skin conditions, recent procedures (laser, filler, Botox — wait 4 weeks), or blood-thinning medications. Minor bruising at facial needle sites is possible and typically resolves in 24–48 hours.`,
