    howItWorks: `Ultra-fine needles are placed at specific points on the face to stimulate collagen synthesis, improve Qi and Blood circulation, lift and tone facial muscles, and reduce inflammation. Body acupuncture points are simultaneously selected to address constitutional factors (digestive health, hormonal balance, nervous system regulation). Sessions run 75–90 minutes. A course of 10–12 weekly sessions, followed by monthly maintenance, constitutes the standard treatment protocol.`,
