    opening: `Chronic stress is not just a psychological experience — it is a physiological cascade that drives cortisol dysregulation, immune suppression, cardiovascular stress, digestive dysfunction, and hormonal imbalance. At Integrative Health Partners, Dr. Hendry treats chronic stress through acupuncture that targets the autonomic nervous system directly — shifting patients from chronic sympathetic over-activation to the parasympathetic state in which healing, digestion, immunity, and sleep are possible.`,
    howItWorks: `Stress-focused acupuncture sessions combine body acupuncture points with specific ear acupuncture (auricular NADA protocol) to produce maximum nervous system regulation. Points are selected to calm the Heart (Shen/mind), regulate Liver Qi (which drives the tension, irritability, and physical constriction of chronic stress), and support Kidney and Adrenal energy. Moxibustion (warming moxa over specific points) is often added for depleted, exhausted patients.`,
