    howItWorks: `Upper back pain treatment combines acupuncture (targeting thoracic paraspinal points, Governing Vessel, and Bladder meridian points) with precise trigger point dry needling of the most common upper back muscle offenders — upper trapezius, rhomboids, infraspinatus, and serratus anterior. Cupping therapy is often added to the upper back for myofascial release and circulation enhancement.`,
