    howItWorks: `Natural medicine consultations follow a comprehensive intake process covering your chief complaints, complete health history, Chinese medical diagnosis, and functional medicine systems review. From this, Dr. Hendry identifies the most appropriate natural medicine interventions — which may include acupuncture, herbal medicine, dietary modification, targeted supplementation, ozone therapy, or injection therapy — and presents a clear, prioritized plan.`,
