    howItWorks: `Menopause treatment combines acupuncture (targeting the HT and KD channels to address the Heart-Kidney disharmony at the core of menopausal heat pattern) with Chinese herbal medicine (particularly Yin-nourishing formulas like Liu Wei Di Huang Wan, Er Xian Tang for mixed deficiency patterns). Functional medicine evaluates the complete hormone panel (estradiol, progesterone, FSH, LH, DHEA-S, testosterone, thyroid) and adrenal function to build an individualized protocol.`,
