    howItWorks: `Acid reflux treatment at IHP combines acupuncture (which reduces esophageal and gastric hypersensitivity, improves LES tone, and promotes gastric emptying), Chinese herbal medicine (particularly Zuo Jin Wan for Liver-invading-Stomach pattern; Ban Xia Xie Xin Tang for Stomach Disharmony), and functional medicine assessment including H. pylori testing, gastric acid level assessment, food sensitivity panel, and SIBO testing.`,
