    howItWorks: `Adrenal fatigue treatment begins with 4-point salivary cortisol testing to map the cortisol rhythm through the day. Based on the curve pattern (high cortisol, inverted curve, flat curve, or various mixed patterns), Dr. Hendry selects the appropriate protocol. Acupuncture targets Kidney Yang tonification (the Chinese medicine pattern corresponding to cortisol deficiency). Adaptogenic herbs (Ren Shen, Huang Qi, Wu Wei Zi, Schisandra) support HPA axis recovery.`,
