    opening: `Nutritional deficiency testing at Integrative Health Partners goes beyond checking a single vitamin D level to provide a comprehensive assessment of your micronutrient status — identifying the specific deficiencies that are contributing to your symptoms and limiting your body's ability to heal. Most chronic conditions have a nutritional deficiency component that is rarely investigated in standard care.`,
